ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: i would definitely recommend the class to another student, for the reasons outlined in my answer to the first question.
yes - for psychology students this is a very good course. May be a bit developmental focused if you are not interested in that area.
yes,- interesting and relevant topics- understandable readings- enlightening discussions- encouraging instructor

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: have already used many of the readings to shed light on current projects.
- added to basic knowledge about the field- showed a number of relevant areas of new research- a lot of useful references
